<A NAME="chapterConvexDecomposition3Ref"></A><h1>Convex Decomposition of Polyhedra<BR>
<I>Reference&nbsp;Manual</I></h1>

 
<p class="subtitle">Peter Hachenberger</p>
<P>

The function <I>convex_decomposition_3</I> takes a
<I><A HREF="../Nef_3_ref/Class_Nef_polyhedron_3.html#Cross_link_anchor_1174">Nef_polyhedron_3</A></I> <span class="math">N</span> as input parameter and inserts additional facets, 
such that each bounded marked volume (the outer volume is unbounded)
is subdivided into convex pieces.
<P>

